                                                <img id="imgUsuario" style="max-width:200px;" src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/D4E03AQGB7uyxtc_y9A/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1712626625641?e=1718236800&v=beta&t=UZR4ysjhZXM8lVnkIOb9Rk99pjtAhAYLw7XmXMJTRBQ" class="rounded mx-auto d-block" alt="Foto usuario">
